{"ts": "2026-06-09T17:43:56.943585+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Here's what this fork's `gita/cmds.json` registers:\n\n| Subcommand | Underlying `git` command | Notes |\n|---|---|---|\n| **br** | `git branch -vv` | Show local branches |\n| **clean** | `git clean -dfx` | Remove all untracked files/folders |\n| **diff** | `git diff` | Show differences |\n| **difftool** | `git difftool` | ⚠️ `disable_async: true` |\n| **fetch** | `git fetch` | ⚠️ `allow_all: true` |\n| **last** | `git log -1 HEAD` | Show log of HEAD |\n| **lo** | `git log --oneline -7` | ⚠️ `allow_all: true` |\n| **log** | `git log` | ⚠️ `disable_async: true` |\n| **merge** | `git merge @{u}` | Merge remote updates |\n| **mergetool** | `git mergetool` | ⚠️ `disable_async: true` |\n| **patch** | `git format-patch HEAD~` | Make a patch |\n| **pull** | `git pull` | ⚠️ `allow_all: true` |\n| **push** | `git push` | ⚠️ `allow_all: true` |\n| **rebase** | `git rebase` | Rebase from master |\n| **reflog** | `git reflog` | Show ref logs |\n| **remote** | `git remote -v` | Show remote settings |\n| **reset** | `git reset` | Reset repo(s) |\n| **show** | `git show` | ⚠️ `disable_async: true` |\n| **stash** | `git stash` | Store uncommitted changes |\n| **stat** | `git diff --stat` | ⚠️ `allow_all: true` |\n| **st** | `git status` | ⚠️ `allow_all: true` |\n| **tag** | `git tag -n` | Show tags |\n\n---\n\n### Entries with special flags\n\n**`allow_all: true`** (6 subcommands) — these are passed through without repo-list gating:\n- `fetch` → `git fetch`\n- `lo` → `git log --oneline -7`\n- `pull` → `git pull`\n- `push` → `git push`\n- `stat` → `git diff --stat`\n- `st` → `git status`\n\n**`disable_async: true`** (4 subcommands) — these are run synchronously (not in parallel across repos), likely because they require interactive terminal I/O:\n- `difftool` → `git difftool`\n- `log` → `git log`\n- `mergetool` → `git mergetool`\n- `show` → `git show`", "additional_kwargs